== Overview ==
The Hydroplasmonic Reactor is a special reactor that can be obtained as a reward for defeating the [[Carnutum Arena Masters]].

== Where to Acquire ==
The Hydroplasmonic Reactor is awarded to the Controller for defeating the Carnutum Arena Masters at the [[Carnutum Ignus Gladiator Areana]] in the [[South West Quadrant]] of [[Gamma]].

